ZH: 感谢您的指点，我一定会努力改进。
EN: Thank you for your guidance, I will definitely work to improve.

ZH: 请赐教如何更好地解决这个问题。
EN: Please advise on how to better solve this problem.

ZH: 他向老师请教，获得了很好的赐教。
EN: He sought advice from the teacher and received very helpful guidance.

ZH: 你有什么好的建议吗？请不吝赐教。
EN: Do you have any good suggestions? Please don't hesitate to advise.

